  <brief_title>Nefopam for Post Video-Assisted Thoracoscopic Lobectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Nefopam for Post Video-Assisted Thoracoscopic Lobectomy Pain Management and the Improvement of Enhanced Recovery After Surgery (ERAS): A Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
